# Configuration Files

## Package Management
- **[package.json](mdc:package.json)** - Project dependencies, scripts, and metadata
  - Key dependencies: Next.js 14, React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
  - Development dependencies: Jest, ESLint, Testing Library
  - Scripts: dev, build, start, lint, test, test:watch

## Framework Configuration
- **[next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs)** - Next.js configuration
- **[tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)** - TypeScript compiler configuration
- **[tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts)** - Tailwind CSS configuration
- **[postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs)** - PostCSS configuration for Tailwind

## Code Quality & Testing
- **[.eslintrc.json](mdc:.eslintrc.json)** - ESLint configuration for code linting
- **[jest.config.js](mdc:jest.config.js)** - Jest testing framework configuration
- **[jest.setup.js](mdc:jest.setup.js)** - Jest setup file for testing environment

## UI Components
- **[components.json](mdc:components.json)** - shadcn/ui components configuration
  - Defines component paths, styling approach, and aliases

## Styling
- **[app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css)** - Global CSS styles and Tailwind directives
- **[app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx)** - Root layout with global styles and fonts

## Version Control
- **[.gitignore](mdc:.gitignore)** - Git ignore patterns for Node.js/Next.js projects

